<p class="ql-align-justify">11月5日上午，南京市江宁实验小学在校举行了以“垃圾分一分 城市美十分”为主题的垃圾分类宣传活动。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><iframe width="500" height="300" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" border="0" allowfullscreen="true" src="//tv.sohu.com/s/sohuplayer/iplay.html?bid=222362012&amp;vars=%5B%5B%22showRecommend%22%2C0%5D%5D&amp;disablePlaylist=true&amp;mute=1&amp;autoplay=false"></iframe></p>
